  description: "The Lamia is a deceptive hunter that lures victims with a soothing
    voice and captivating appearance. \nShe takes pleasure in creating fear. Her
    prey is most commonly men and children. \n\nCaution is advised, as her appearance
    and her hypnotic voice can easily lead the unwary astray.  "
